@page
@model ErrorModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Error";
}

<h1 class="text-danger">
    @*Error.*@
    Fejl.
</h1>
<h2 class="text-danger">
    @*An error occurred while processing your request.*@
    En fejl opstod under behandlingen af din anmodning.
</h2>

@if (Model.ShowRequestId)
{
    <p>
        <strong>Request ID:</strong> <code>@Model.RequestId</code>
    </p>
}

<h3>
    @*Development Mode*@
    Udviklingsmåde
</h3>
<p>
    @*Swapping to the <strong>Development</strong> environment displays detailed information about the error that occurred.*@
    Bytte til <strong> Udvikling </strong> -miljøet viser detaljerede oplysninger om den fejl, der opstod.
</p>
<p>
    @*<strong>The Development environment shouldn't be enabled for deployed applications.</strong>
        It can result in displaying sensitive information from exceptions to end users.
        For local debugging, enable the <strong>Development</strong> environment by setting the <strong>ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT</strong> environment variable to <strong>Development</strong>
        and restarting the app.*@
    <strong>
        Udviklingsmiljøet bør ikke aktiveres for implementerede applikationer.</strong>
    Det kan resultere i at vise følsomme oplysninger fra undtagelser til slutbrugere.
    Hvis du vil lokal fejlfinding, skal du aktivere miljøet <strong>Udvikling</strong> ved at indstille miljøvariablen
    <strong>ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT</strong> til <strong>Udvikling</strong>og genstart appen.
</p>
